// DEPENDS ON MYSQL TIMEZONE TABLES FOR PROPER TIMEZONE CONVERSION
For Ubuntu, for example, run:
    $: mysql_tzinfo_to_sql /usr/share/zoneinfo | mysql -u root -p mysql
Type in the password. If you don't have /usr/share/zoneinfo, check your distribution to
see where the system timezone locations are stored.